      <title>posquit0/Awesome-CV</title>
      <link>https://github.com/posquit0/Awesome-CV</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;📄 Awesome CV is LaTeX template for your outstanding job application&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;h1 align=&quot;center&quot;&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/posquit0/Awesome-CV&quot; title=&quot;AwesomeCV Documentation&quot;&gt; &lt;img alt=&quot;AwesomeCV&quot; src=&quot;https://github.com/posquit0/Awesome-CV/raw/master/icon.png&quot; width=&quot;200px&quot; height=&quot;200px&quot; /&gt; &lt;/a&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Awesome CV &lt;/h1&gt; 
